			<Text>Each source of [ICON_RES_WHALE] Whales, [ICON_RES_COAL] Coal, [ICON_RES_OIL] Oil, and [ICON_RES_URANIUM] Uranium worked by this City produces +2 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production.</Text>
